INSERT INTO usage (
            api_key_id, model_id, user_id,
            total_tokens
        )
        SELECT
            ak.api_key_id, m.model_id, ak.user_id,
            $3
        FROM
            (
                SELECT api_key_id, user_id
                FROM api_keys
                WHERE api_key = $1
            ) ak
        JOIN
            (
                SELECT model_id
                FROM models
                WHERE model_name = $2
            ) m ON true
        JOIN
            users u ON u.user_id = ak.user_id AND u.usage_tracking_enabled = true
